'''周亚辉'''（{{bd|1977年|2月||}}）是[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]][[亿万富翁|亿万富翁]]以及企业家。2008年，他创立了中国最大网络游戏开发商之一的昆仑万维<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-05-29|title=China's Kunlun says U.S approves sale of Grindr to investor group|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-grindr-m-a-sanvincente-idUSKBN2352PR|accessdate=2020-08-31|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209103905/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-grindr-m-a-sanvincente-idUSKBN2352PR|dead-url=no}}</ref>，直到2020年他一直担任該公司的董事长兼首席执行官。此後周亚辉担任[[Opera軟件|Opera軟件]]董事长兼联合首席执行官。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Unveiled! Yahui Zhou, 42-Year Old Chinese Billionaire is Behind the Opay Revolution in Nigeria|url=https://www.financialtechnologyafrica.com/2019/11/14/unveiled-yahui-zhou-42-year-old-chinese-billionaire-is-behind-the-opay-revolution-in-nigeria/|accessdate=2020-08-31|date=2019-11-14|work=Financial Technology|language=en-US}}</ref>他的净资产估计为22亿美元。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Zhou Yahui|url=https://www.forbes.com/profile/zhou-yahui-1/|accessdate=2019-03-03|work=Forbes|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027221532/https://www.forbes.com/profile/zhou-yahui-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

